{"tid":1777624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪拜感謝各位課金，誠邀大家12/12出黎監察我地啲錢洗左去邊","createTime":"2019-12-10T10:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T11:27:15.000Z","uid":264429,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"6872edb18d078581d8344c59fefacd973da5c698","tid":1777624,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"首先多謝大家喺上一個Post積極支持我地民間集會團隊，令我地一日多啲已籌到超過30萬，衷心感謝！<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n[雪地插J求助] 頂左六個月，民間集會團隊實在頂唔住要眾籌，求大家捐少少<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776047</a><br />\n眾籌連結： <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=ffaad706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟動眾籌之後，我地第一個做既集會將會係<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">12.12齊上齊落、612半週年集會</span></strong>，已獲popo發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n因為有你地既支持，我地已經同音響手足溝通，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求佢地當日加碼音響，務求當日成個愛丁堡廣場都要清楚聽到個台講乜</span></strong>，唔要再好似之前咁，全場大叫聽唔到。<br />\n<br />\n懇請各位到時出席，好好監察下我地啲錢用左去邊，音響有無改善到。更重要係，繼續聚人集氣，話比政府同全世界聽，我地612至今半年，仍然堅持，無放棄過！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">1212 愛丁堡見</span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdaqNBK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdaqNBK.jpg&h=ca79c61e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zr2QegK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZr2QegK.jpg&h=40333b8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygbhDJq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygbhDJq.jpg&h=f06e1e7c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJWJzgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJWJzgM.jpg&h=cb1853a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8d5998e34d4d9b0fdf43bd5484c5c3b6e35c34d","tid":1777624,"uid":249263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:44:42.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=a00a444e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"10fd3fd03ccec10fc7f42efca8ac6e45eb120e37","tid":1777624,"uid":277934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea22711620d9faec14db4f2911e98f82d432133","tid":1777624,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:45:14.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀"},{"pid":"d844cf5a9f9dacdef0937360694f4e84aa663708","tid":1777624,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 